<plot>The movie takes it's shape when Conner crashes his old station wagon on an abandon road during a rain storm. Before long he is greeted by Jamie, a suitcase carrying stranger. Conner offers her shelter from the rain and they both wait for rescue. As the two find out more about each other they also find there's more to their chance meeting than meets the eye.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?160396</url></doc>
